if daemon true
python boxnya.py start|stop|restar

input->filter->output
or
input->output

example
input:twitter,gmail
filter:egosearch
output:imkayac

INOUT = {"twitter":["egosearch"],
         "egosearch":["imkayac"],
         "gmail":["imkayac"]
         }
         
settings
key:module(input,output or filter) name
value:args dictionary or list
if list and list contains plural value, that module is cloned.

example
twitter has 2 settings.
so, 2 twitter module run.
you can use more than one account. 
INPUT_SETTINGS = {
                  "gmail":{"username":"", "password":""},
                  "twitter":[{"atoken":"","atokensecret":""},
                             {"atoken":"","atokensecret":""}],
                  }